Date: January 30th 2024

Summary: LEVEL 52: THE SCHOOL HALLS: AI unable to guide through level

Priority or Severity: A

Visibility: High

Type: AI

Reproduction Rate: 100%

Description: When a player blocks the guiding AI at a double doorway, the AI programming will bug out, resulting in the AI not moving further, making the level impossible to beat

Launch the title
Make your way through the game until Level 52
Make your way through the level until you reach a double-door
Stand in front of the AI

Result: When standing in front of the AI, the AI can no longer move

Expected result: After moving when standing in front of the AI, the AI will proceed down its programmed path 
